download folder
npm install
ng serve --open / npm start

install json server  -> npm install -g json-server
create local folder-> create db.json file , with your json data
refernce link --> https://github.com/typicode/json-server
db.json looks like below
{
  "employees": [
    {
      "id": 111,
      "firstname": "Adarsha",
      "lastname": "sharma",
      "email": "Adasrh@gmail.com"
    },
    ]
 }

run json server --> json-server --watch db.json


 
